"./Scientific_Research_Publishing" title="Scientific Research Publishing">Scientific Research Publishing</a>.</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable" about="#mwt2" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"hatnote","href":"./Template:Hatnote"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"Compare [[Observational study]] and [[Experiment]]"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAw">Compare <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Observational_study" title="Observational study">Observational study</a> and <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Experiment" title="Experiment">Experiment</a></div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable" about="#mwt3" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"other uses","href":"./Template:Other_uses"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"Scientific method (disambiguation)"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBA">For other uses, see <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Scientific_method_(disambiguation)" title="Scientific method (disambiguation)">Scientific method (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
